 Conclusion:
This project presents a complete end-to-end machine learning pipeline for
predicting product reorders and time to next order using Instacart data.
Through extensive preprocessing, feature engineering, model evaluation,
and robustness testing, the results demonstrate the effectiveness of
tree-based and gradient boosting models. The project emphasizes
reproducibility, interpretability, and adherence to the DS230 course
requirements.